This release ships derived analytical artefacts (parquet, JSONL, CSV,
JSON) computed from the cukereuse step corpus
(https://github.com/amughalbscs16/cukereuse-release). The underlying
.feature-file bodies are NOT included in this distribution and remain
subject to their respective upstream licences as recorded in the
per-step license_spdx column of the cukereuse corpus. See
DATA_CARD.md for the full provenance discussion.

Author-produced labels in methodology/labels.jsonl carry an explicit
labeler field (A / B / C) and the rubric clause that fired per row.
Labels were applied directly by the three named authors against the
written rubric in methodology/LABELING_RUBRIC_paper2_slice_level.md.
